 class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησεν\">ἒζη[σε]ν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ιγ´ ❦ \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\">ἐποίησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">Εὐοδία\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μνήμης\">μνήμης\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χάριν\">χάριν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)\u003C/span> ❦ ⸙ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>❦\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">ΚΑΤΥΛΛΕΙΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησεν\">ΕΖΗ[..]Ν\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΙΓ❦\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">ΕΥΟΔΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μνήμης\">ΜΝΗΜΗΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χάριν\">ΧΑΡΙΝ\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;❦⸙\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003224_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003224_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003224.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003224-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Castelli read the text without the lacuna, but according to Korhonen, this is a not recorded supplement by the previous editors\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Katylleinos lived for 13 years. Eudoia made (this) for his memory\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Katylleinos visse per 13 anni. Euodia fece (questo) in sua memoria.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>According to Korhonen, the form of this epitaph is one of the most common in Catania, with two main sentences, the first containing the name of the deceased and his age, the second the indication of the dedicant with the aorist of \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ποιέω\u003C/span>, which in this case precedes the name of the dedicant, as in IG 14.467 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001291\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001291\u003C/a>. For this reason, Korhonen rejects Kaibel’s classification (adopted by Moretti in IGUR) of this inscription among the urban inscriptions. The expression \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">μνήμης χάριν\u003C/span> occurs in many epitaphs from Catania: e.g. IG 14.485 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001308\" target=\"_blank\">ISic00001308\u003C/a>, IG 14.509 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001330\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001330\u003C/a>, IG 14.511 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001332\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001332\u003C/a>. The name of the deceased, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Κατυλλεῖνος\u003C/span>, recurs also in an inscription from Syracuse: SEG 36.862 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001650\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001650\u003C/a>. \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐοδία\u003C/span> could be the mother of the young deceased: the name is possibly found in an inscription from Syracuse (Agnello 1960: no.39 + Ferrua 1989: no.243).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Franz 1853 5711 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">1745\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Moretti 1968-1990 670 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000015\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000015\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 68 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Letters with small apices, lunate Ε and Σ, cursive Μ. Four ivy-leaves and a palmette.\u003C/p> Lines 1-5  11-15  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[231,234,237,240,243,245,248,251,254],{"id":232,"html":233},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>❦ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">Κατυλλεῖνος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησεν\">ἒζη[σε]ν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ιγ´ ❦ \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\">ἐποίησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">Εὐοδία\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μνήμης\">μνήμης\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χάριν\">χάριν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)\u003C/span> ❦ ⸙ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>❦\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">ΚΑΤΥΛΛΕΙΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησεν\">ΕΖΗ[..]Ν\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΙΓ❦\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">ΕΥΟΔΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μνήμης\">ΜΝΗΜΗΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χάριν\">ΧΑΡΙΝ\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;❦⸙\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":235,"html":236},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003224_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003224_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003224.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003224-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":238,"html":239},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Castelli read the text without the lacuna, but according to Korhonen, this is a not recorded supplement by the previous editors\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":241,"html":242},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Katylleinos lived for 13 years. Eudoia made (this) for his memory\u003C/p>  ",{"id":241,"html":244},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Katylleinos visse per 13 anni. Euodia fece (questo) in sua memoria.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":246,"html":247},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>According to Korhonen, the form of this epitaph is one of the most common in Catania, with two main sentences, the first containing the name of the deceased and his age, the second the indication of the dedicant with the aorist of \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ποιέω\u003C/span>, which in this case precedes the name of the dedicant, as in IG 14.467 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001291\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001291\u003C/a>. For this reason, Korhonen rejects Kaibel’s classification (adopted by Moretti in IGUR) of this inscription among the urban inscriptions. The expression \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">μνήμης χάριν\u003C/span> occurs in many epitaphs from Catania: e.g. IG 14.485 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001308\" target=\"_blank\">ISic00001308\u003C/a>, IG 14.509 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001330\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001330\u003C/a>, IG 14.511 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001332\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001332\u003C/a>. The name of the deceased, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Κατυλλεῖνος\u003C/span>, recurs also in an inscription from Syracuse: SEG 36.862 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001650\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001650\u003C/a>. \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐοδία\u003C/span> could be the mother of the young deceased: the name is possibly found in an inscription from Syracuse (Agnello 1960: no.39 + Ferrua 1989: no.243).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":249,"html":250},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Franz 1853 5711 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">1745\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Moretti 1968-1990 670 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000015\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000015\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 68 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":252,"html":253},"handnote","\u003Cp>Letters with small apices, lunate Ε and Σ, cursive Μ. Four ivy-leaves and a palmette.\u003C/p> Lines 1-5  11-15  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":255,"html":256},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[258,260,263,264],{"html":259},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou",{"id":261,"lang":122,"html":262},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>❦ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">Κατυλλεῖνος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησεν\">ἒζη[σε]ν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ιγ´ ❦ \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\">ἐποίησεν\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐοδία\">Εὐοδία\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μνήμης\">μνήμης\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χάριν\">χάριν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)\u003C/span> ❦ ⸙ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":259},{"id":265,"lang":122,"html":266},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>❦\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κατυλλεῖνος\">ΚΑΤΥΛΛΕΙΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησεν\">ΕΖΗ[..]Ν\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">ΕΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΙΓ❦\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003